entities.name: constant-combinator
entities.player_description:
This is here to keep track of the number of un-allocated Depot stops.  Every time a train is built, decrement the count.  Every time a Depot Hub is built, increase it by the number of depots in that print.

Using this regularly will give an indication of when a new Depot Hub needs to be built somewhere in the factory, preferrably as far away from existing hubs as is practical.
